<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Market Assistant Platform</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Market Assistant Platform</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining Market Assistant Platform! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
    <p>With our platform, you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access real-time market data and analytics</li>
      <li>Get AI-powered trading insights</li>
      <li>Set up custom alerts and notifications</li>
      <li>Analyze market trends with advanced charting tools</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    <p>Happy trading!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Market Assistant Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Market Assistant. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>If you didn't create an account, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
